            "description": "Restore a prototype 'Export backup' JSON. `items`→Contact (status→stage, reply→accepted, note→a note Activity), `targets`→Company, `apps`→Application. Contacts link to a company by matching name. `?mode=replace` wipes the user's existing data first; `merge` (default) appends."
          },
